title: Jagged alliance back in action save game edit mod tool
description:
Jagged alliance back in action save game edit mod tool
=======================================================

Simple application for modding your Jagged Alliance back in action save games.
This will upgrade your weapons, armor and tools and upskill your team to 100% in all areas.

Its still in development at the moment, so make sure you backup your save game files first.

I have only tested this on 1.13g but it should work on other versions also.
have fun!
